attributeList.attribute: Non-coding RNA containing complex that is involved in mRNA splicing. The U4/U6 x U5 tri-snRNP complex binds to the pre-spliceosome complex to form the pre-activation complex. The spliceosome is a highly dynamic structure, assembled by sequential binding and release of the small nuclear RNAs and protein factors which removes intronic sequence from pre-mRNA.
